    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(FYI - Before you buy this experience, I fully understand the condition of it is not perfect. I'm a solo developer so if you have bought this, thankyou so much! It will help me continue my journey, and before you know it, I'll be back on this, to make it a fun, cohesive and memorable experience. In the meantime, enjoy life to the fullest and keep learning to be the best you can be! Take care! PLB x)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DESCRIPTION</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're a Tubby. A specially designed sentient that just loves to test. You've been assigned to Artem. An art gallery full of problems that could arise in the real world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're here to be the best, and show what's possible, ensuring the public safety in the future if you're ever assigned to the <strong>Outside.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Your aim</strong></u> - <i>Keep everything as it was before the test ends.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Put out fires.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Correct the cables.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Reboot the cameras.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Keep that air filter on!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Realign the paintings.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Return the sculptures.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Clean up any mess.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>And if you get a spare moment, earn a heck of a bonus with the simple brain training computer tasks, to bump that basic pay, so you can  style yourself as the cutest lil' Tubby you are.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's <strong>puzzling management chaos</strong>, but with over <strong><i>50 wearable items</i></strong>, each with its individual look, you'll want to buy them all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >So...Get to work Tubby!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MULTIPLAYER COMING SOON! (I'm a solo dev, so still figuring that out)</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Go to Work</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras/6df38e695a4f847e06f75f411402054e.avif?t=1738677337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras_big/6df38e695a4f847e06f75f411402054e.avif?t=1738677337 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Fix Problems</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras/a3261c90719931607e087761ad935e55.avif?t=1738677337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras_big/a3261c90719931607e087761ad935e55.avif?t=1738677337 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Press Buttons</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras/b94dab2008a6fd93f1f4e2d39add868c.avif?t=1738677337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras_big/b94dab2008a6fd93f1f4e2d39add868c.avif?t=1738677337 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Earn Your Bonus</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras/f85a5384e8bb69239f4e187c8562dc07.avif?t=1738677337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras_big/f85a5384e8bb69239f4e187c8562dc07.avif?t=1738677337 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Style It Out</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras/adb1c72b9134747b04b65dfe2fdda2ad.avif?t=1738677337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299620/extras_big/adb1c72b9134747b04b65dfe2fdda2ad.avif?t=1738677337 width=800 height=800 /></span></p>",
